flowchart TD
    A[Under review or resubmitted] --> B{At least one submitted review?}
    B -->|no| B1[Stay in review stage]
    B -->|yes| C[AE opens Exit Review Stage]
    C --> D[Auto-cancel selected, invited, opened]
    C --> E{Accepted but not submitted reviewers}
    E -->|wait| B1
    E -->|all handled| F{Target stage}
    D --> F
    F -->|first| G[Decision queue]
    F -->|final| H[Decision done queue]
    G --> I[First Decision: major, minor, reject]
    H --> J[Final Decision]
    J -->|accept| K[Production and Finance]
    J -->|major, minor, reject| L[Revision or reject]
    I --> L
    K --> M[Publish]
